[0.521, "o", "\r\n\r\nTwo all-privilege accounts were created.\r\nOne is root@localhost, it has no password, but you need to\r\nbe system 'root' user to connect. Use, for example, sudo mariadb\r\nThe second is mysql@localhost, it has no password either, but\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "you need to be the system 'mysql' user to connect.\r\nAfter connecting you can set the password, if you would need to be\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "able to connect as any of these users with a password and without sudo\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "See the MariaDB Knowledgebase at https://mariadb.com/kb\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Please report any problems at https://mariadb.org/jira\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "The latest information about MariaDB is available at https://mariadb.org/.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Consider joining MariaDB's strong and vibrant community:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "https://mariadb.org/get-involved/\r\n\r\n"]
